      pear/DB/fbsql.php
      pear/DB/mssql.php
      pear/DB/mysql.php
      pear/DB/oci8.php
      pear/DB/odbc.php
      pear/DB/pgsql.php:
    * the actual name of the sequences or sequence emulation tables may
      now be configured with the "seqname_format" option

    * pear/package.dtd: * add some missing attributes

